<h2 class="gem-c-heading  gem-c-heading--mobile-top-margin  " id="details-title">Details</h2>


<div aria-labelledby="details-title">
  
<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak direction-ltr" data-module="govspeak">
      <div class="govspeak">
<p>The White Paper confirms that the EU (Withdrawal Agreement) Bill will:</p>

<ul>
  <li>be the primary means by which the rights of EU citizens will be protected in UK law;</li>
  <li>legislate for the time-limited implementation period; and</li>
  <li>create a financial authority to manage the specific payments to be made under the financial settlement, with appropriate Parliamentary oversight</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>

